umina_image_box image=\"65\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center; font-size: 150%; line-height: 100%;\"><span style=\"color: #ffffff;\">Claim</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center; font-size: 250%; line-height: 100%;\"><span style=\"color: #ffffff;\"><strong>$3,200</strong></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center; font-size: 200; line-height: 100%;\"><span style=\"color: #ffffff;\">Meowington suffered a broken leg jumping out of a window.</span></p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_column_text]\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><span style=\"color: #3c78b4; font-size: 150%;\">WHAT IS PETSHIELD INSURANCE?</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">We know those little furry friends are part of the family too, PetShield insurance helps cover the cost of veterinary treatments in the event of an insured pet falling ill or being injured in an accident.</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">Some policies may cover and pay if your pet dies,Â lost or stolen or even if it causes injury to a third party or damages to a third partyâs property.</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">Our policies are not limited to cats or dogs, many of our plans and policies covers a wide variety of furry friends including exotic, farm and birds.</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><span style=\"color: #3c78b4; font-size: 150%;\">WHY PETSHIELD INSURANCE?</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">Our four legged friends are a big part of our lives, so when they fall ill or injured, we know providing the best health care for them is important.</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">With the advances in veterinary medicine, treatments are now available that were once reserved for humans, making curable conditions that were once fatal in animals, Inevitably, these types of treatments and diagnostics come at a price, leaving some owners faced with a difficult choice.</p>\r\nFor this reason, PetShield offers policies that provide valuable peace of mind against variable vet fees and it also allows owners to explore available treatment options.\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><span style=\"color: #3c78b4; font-size: 150%;\">WHAT IS THE COST OF PETSHIELD INSURANCE?</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">As with any form of insurance, PetShield calculate our pet policies with a variety of factors such as, breed, age and gender, the sort of products selected, if your petâs been micro chipped, zip code (may vary in rural or urban areas), pedigree, pre-existing medical conditions and if you want a premium coverage.</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">PetShield offers a wide range of policies with different coverages, some of the plans we offer are:</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">â¢ Accident Only Policies</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">â¢ Time Limited Policies</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">â¢ Maximum Benefits Policies</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">â¢ Lifetime/Covered for Life Policies</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">â¢ Premium policy</p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row\" css=\".vc_custom_1506484161769{background-color: #3c78b4 !important;}\"][vc_column][vc_column_text]\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><span style=\"color: #ffffff;\"><strong>PETSHIELD HAS YOUR FURRY FRIENDS COVERED IN THE FOLLOWING STATES</strong></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><span style=\"color: #ffffff; font-size: 75%;\">We can provide you with Pet Insurance in all the 50 states:</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><span style=\"color: #ffffff; font-size: 75%;\">Alabama AL,Alaska AK,Arizona AZ,Arkansas AR,California CA,Colorado CO,Connecticut CT,Delaware DE,Florida FL,Georgia GA,Hawaii HI,Idaho ID,Illinois IL,Indiana IN,Iowa IA,Kansas KS,Kentucky KY,Louisiana LA,Maine ME,Maryland MD,Massachusetts MA,Michigan MI,Minnesota MN,Mississippi MS,Missouri MO,Montana MT,Nebraska NE,Nevada NV,New Hampshire NH,New Jersey NJ,New Mexico NM,New York NY,North Carolina NC,North Dakota ND,Ohio OH,Oklahoma OK,Oregon OR,Pennsylvania PA,Rhode Island RI,South Carolina SC,South Dakota SD,Tennessee TN,Texas TX,Utah UT,Vermont VT,Virginia VA,Washington WA,West Virginia WV,Wisconsin WI,Wyoming WY</span></p>\r\n